            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When the party contains at least 4 characters,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Elemental Resonance Effects",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "corresponding to the Elemental Types present in the party will be provided.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Elemental Resonance can be found in any Party Setup (Overworld, Abyss, Domain)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When 2 characters of the same elemental type are in the party, the corresponding element's Resonance Effect will become active. There is also a unique Resonance effect when there are 4 unique elements in the party. In this way, the maximum number of Elemental Resonances for any team is 2.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Requirements",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "items": [
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "The party must have at least 4 characters.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "The maximum number of Elemental Resonance present in the part is 2.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "To activate any Elemental Resonance except",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "styles": [
                              "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                            ],
                            "text": "Protective Canopy",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": ", 2+ characters of the specific Element are needed.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "Trial characters can also be considered for Elemental Resonance. When there are more than 4 characters in the party, only the first 4 characters will be considered for Elemental Resonance.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "Inside domains, only the characters present in the party will benefit from Elemental Resonance effects.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "Elemental Resonance will activate in Co-op mode as long as the requirements are met.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
